<div class="column_2_article">
    <h3>MCLab</h3>

    <p>MC Lab is powerful laboratory information management systems (LIMS) designed specially for laboratory automation in rubber industry taking into account summarised requirements and wishes of users, technicians and management from the different rubber companies.</p>
    <img src="images/lab_interface_1.png" alt="lab_interface_1">
